<i>noun</i>: 행위 [행위], 행동 [행동], 처분 [처ː분], 조치 [조치], 조처 [조처], 작용 [자굥], 액션 [], 실천 [실천], 몸동작 [몸똥작], 대책 [대ː책], 대응책 [대ː응책], 걸음 [거름] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>행위 [행위]</dt><br>
<dd>act; action; conduct; deed</dd><br>
<dd>사람이 의지를 가지고 하는 짓.</dd><br>
<dd>An act done with an intention or will.</dd><br>
<dt>행동 [행동]</dt><br>
<dd>action; movement behavior; deed</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 움직여 어떤 일이나 동작을 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of moving one's body to do a certain task or action.</dd><br>
<dt>처분 [처ː분]</dt><br>
<dd>1. disposal</dd><br>
<dd>물건이나 재산 등을 처리하여 치움.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of disposing of objects, assets, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. measure; action</dd><br>
<dd>일을 어떻게 처리할 것인가에 대해 지시하거나 결정함. 또는 그런 지시나 결정.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of ordering or deciding how to handle something, or such an order or decision.</dd><br>
<dd>3. measure; action</dd><br>
<dd>행정, 사법 관청이 특별한 사건에 대해 법규를 적용하여 처리하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act by a government or administrative office of handling a special case by applying certain laws.</dd><br>
<dt>조치 [조치]</dt><br>
<dd>action; step; measure</dd><br>
<dd>벌어진 사태에 대하여 적절한 대책을 세워서 행함. 또는 그 대책.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of developing and implementing an adequate solution to an issue, or such solution.</dd><br>
<dt>조처 [조처]</dt><br>
<dd>step; action</dd><br>
<dd>문제가 된 상황이나 일을 잘 처리함. 또는 그러한 방식.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of resolving a problematic situation or issue well, or a way of such resolution.</dd><br>
<dt>작용 [자굥]</dt><br>
<dd>working; function; action</dd><br>
<dd>어떠한 현상이나 행동을 일으키거나 영향을 줌.</dd><br>
<dd>The process of causing or affecting a certain phenomenon or act.</dd><br>
<dt>액션 []</dt><br>
<dd>action</dd><br>
<dd>배우가 특정한 연기를 위해 하는 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>An array of actions done by an actor or actress to perform a certain scene.</dd><br>
<dt>실천 [실천]</dt><br>
<dd>practice; action</dd><br>
<dd>이론이나 계획, 생각한 것을 실제 행동으로 옮김.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of putting one's theory, plan, thought, etc. into action.</dd><br>
<dt>몸동작 [몸똥작]</dt><br>
<dd>body motion; body movement; action</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>The manner of moving a body.</dd><br>
<dt>대책 [대ː책]</dt><br>
<dd>measure; action</dd><br>
<dd>어려운 상황을 이겨낼 수 있는 계획.</dd><br>
<dd>A plan that enables one to overcome a difficult situation.</dd><br>
<dt>대응책 [대ː응책]</dt><br>
<dd>countermeasure; action</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 상황에 알맞은 태도나 행동을 취하기 위한 대책.</dd><br>
<dd>A measure for adopting the appropriate attitude or taking the appropriate action in a certain situation.</dd><br>
<dt>걸음 [거름]</dt><br>
<dd>1. step; walk</dd><br>
<dd>다리를 움직여 두 발을 번갈아 옮겨 놓는 동작.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of moving legs and feet forward one after the other.</dd><br>
<dd>2. visit</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 곳을 방문하는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of visiting a certain place.</dd><br>
<dd>3. action; initiative</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 행동이나 활동 또는 결정.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) An act, activity, or decision.</dd><br>
<dd>4. step</dd><br>
<dd>두 발을 번갈아 옮겨 놓는 횟수를 세는 단위.</dd><br>
<dd>The unit for counting the movement of two feet.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>